msgid ""
"In June 2024, Malaysia implemented a targeted diesel subsidy policy aimed at "
"reducing government expenditure and ensuring that subsidies benefit those "
"most in need. Prior to this reform, diesel was heavily subsidized, leading "
"to significant financial burdens on the government."
msgstr ""
"Pada Jun 2024, Malaysia melaksanakan dasar subsidi diesel bersasar yang "
"bertujuan mengurangkan perbelanjaan kerajaan dan memastikan subsidi memberi "
"manfaat kepada golongan yang paling memerlukan. Sebelum reformasi ini, "
"diesel disubsidi secara besar-besaran, menyebabkan beban kewangan yang besar "
"kepada kerajaan."

